3. cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper discusses the use of the tensor nuclear norm and its partial sum as convex surrogates for the tubal-rank, which is related to information theory and signal processing. 
4. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper presents numerical experiments to evaluate the effectiveness of the proposed methods, which involves numerical analysis and optimization.
